{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/100333", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/100333/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/100333/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/100333/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/100333", "id": 1333570014, "node_id": "I_kwDOAAsO6M5PfKne", "number": 100333, "title": "No error on cfg as InnerAttribute", "user": {"login": "zommiommy", "id": 25117939, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjI1MTE3OTM5", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/25117939?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/zommiommy", "html_url": "https://github.com/zommiommy", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zommiommy/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zommiommy/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zommiommy/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zommiommy/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zommiommy/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zommiommy/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zommiommy/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zommiommy/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zommiommy/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 650731663, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWw2NTA3MzE2NjM=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/C-bug", "name": "C-bug", "color": "f5f1fd", "default": false, "description": "Category: This is a bug."}], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 2, "created_at": "2022-08-09T17:32:49Z", "updated_at": "2022-08-10T08:01:58Z", "closed_at": "2022-08-10T08:01:58Z", "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "Hi!\r\nI erroneously wrote a `cfg` attribute as an inner attribute `#![` instead of an outer attribute `#[`.\r\n\r\nHere's a simplified example working example:\r\n```rust\r\n#![no_std]\r\n\r\n#[cfg(feature=\"alloc\")]\r\nuse core::*;\r\n\r\npub fn square(num: i32) -> i32 {\r\n    num * num\r\n}\r\n```\r\nand here the **problematic** example:\r\n```rust\r\n#![no_std]\r\n\r\n#![cfg(feature=\"alloc\")] // <----\r\nuse core::*;\r\n\r\npub fn square(num: i32) -> i32 {\r\n    num * num\r\n}\r\n```\r\nThis code still compiles but the function `square` won't be present in the final binary.\r\n\r\nEven weirder, if I cross-compile it to a target that doesn't support `std` it seems to ignore the `#![no_std]:\r\n`cargo check --target=nvptx64-nvidia-cuda`:\r\n```\r\nerror[E0463]: can't find crate for `std`\r\n  |\r\n  = note: the `nvptx64-nvidia-cuda` target may not support the standard library\r\n  = note: `std` is required by `<unknown>` because it does not declare `#![no_std]`\r\n\r\nerror: aborting due to previous error\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Meta\r\n`rustc --version --verbose`:\r\n```\r\nrustc 1.65.0-nightly (f03ce3096 2022-08-08)\r\nbinary: rustc\r\ncommit-hash: f03ce30962cf1b2a5158667eabae8bf6e8d1cb03\r\ncommit-date: 2022-08-08\r\nhost: x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu\r\nrelease: 1.65.0-nightly\r\nLLVM version: 14.0.6\r\n```\r\n\r\nThank you for your work! And thanks to @Soveu for helping debugging this Issue.", "closed_by": {"login": "zommiommy", "id": 25117939, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjI1MTE3OTM5", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/25117939?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/zommiommy", "html_url": "https://github.com/zommiommy", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zommiommy/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zommiommy/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zommiommy/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.git